== 未來發展 ==
===士嘉堡延線項目===

[[士嘉堡輕鐵|士嘉堡輕鐵]]現有ICTS Mark I系列車的車齡日增，但廠商[[龐巴迪運輸|龐巴迪運輸]]已停產該款列車，逼使TTC和多倫多市政府考慮解決方案。多倫多市議會於2014年通過將布魯亞－丹佛線從[[堅尼地站|堅尼地站]]伸延至士嘉堡中心，並於此後關閉士嘉堡輕鐵<ref name="TTC Report 2014 scar ext">{{cite web |url=https://www.ttc.ca/About_the_TTC/Commission_reports_and_information/Commission_meetings/2014/June_24/Reports/Scarborough_Subway_Extension_Update.pdf |publisher=Toronto Transit Commission |title=Toronto Transit Commission Report No. ?? – Scarborough_Subway_Extension_Update |format=PDF |page=1 |date=June 24, 2014 |accessdate=2014-10-30 |archive-date=2014-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031034353/https://www.ttc.ca/About_the_TTC/Commission_reports_and_information/Commission_meetings/2014/June_24/Reports/Scarborough_Subway_Extension_Update.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Scarborough Subway Approved by City Council">{{cite news |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/toronto/14000/article19473790/?page=all |title=A Scarborough Subway: Do the Numbers Add Up? |newspaper=[[環球郵報|The Globe and Mail]] |page=1 |date=July 4, 2014 |accessdate=2014-11-05 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208184705/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/toronto/14000/article19473790/?page=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>。市議會再於2017年3月通過延線採用麥高雲道（{{lang|en|McCowan Road}}）走線，並不於堅尼地站和[[士嘉堡中心站|士嘉堡中心站]]之間另設車站以減低項目造價<ref name="SSE Fast Facts">{{cite web |url=http://www.scarboroughsubwayextension.ca/fast-facts.html |publisher=多倫多市政府、TTC |title=Scarborough Subway Extension: Fast Facts |accessdate=2018-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118161517/http://www.scarboroughsubwayextension.ca/fast-facts.html |archive-date=2018-01-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。延線全長{{convert|6.2|km}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ttc.ca/About_the_TTC/Projects/Scarborough_Subway_P/index.jsp |publisher=TTC |title=TTC Scarborough Subway Extension Project |accessdate=2018-01-24 |archive-date=2018-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126004640/http://www.ttc.ca/About_the_TTC/Projects/Scarborough_Subway_P/index.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，具體造價尚未確定，但目前估計達33.5億加元<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2017/11/22/city-staff-say-updated-scarborough-subway-costs-wont-be-published-until-after-2018-election.html |title=Updated Scarborough subway costs won't be published until after 2018 election |newspaper=《[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]》 |date=2017-11-22 |accessdate=2018-01-24 |first=Jennifer |last=Pagliaro |archive-date=2018-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125074607/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2017/11/22/city-staff-say-updated-scarborough-subway-costs-wont-be-published-until-after-2018-election.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，暫定於2026年第二季開通<ref name="SSE Fast Facts"/>。

